  "2228490": {
    "name": "Atomic Owl",
    "steam_appid": 2228490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/d01587a1ba54b5f315d38ec5379c3e6f.avif?t=1762482262\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as Hidalgo, the last free Bladewing, on a challenging, retro inspired quest to save your corrupted friends and take down the twisted Crow Sorcerer, Omega Wing.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Judanest is unraveling, poisoned by Meza, and broken by betrayal. You awaken after two years, bound to an eternal tree and armed with a demonic, talking blade that may be your only ally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/024cbdcee0310962f8214f134f5f342c.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/024cbdcee0310962f8214f134f5f342c.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/024cbdcee0310962f8214f134f5f342c.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro-Inspired Platforming</strong> and Precision Gameplay!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat hordes of deadly Tengu</strong> in fast-paced, skill-driven combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Die, retry, grow stronger,</strong> and overcome impossible odds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice-acted cast</strong> and charming performances.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Absorb Meza souls</strong> to unlock powerful upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wield the Yutameta scythe</strong> and strike from afar.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your weapon</strong> – Hammer, Blade, or Whip? Your choice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully animated opening cutscene</strong> sets the tone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Transform into the Void Crow</strong> and demolish the Tengu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a vibrant world</strong> full of color and personality.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take flight and glide</strong> through expansive sections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect elemental powers</strong> – Flame, Lightning, and Poison!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A hybrid soundtrack</strong> mixing synthwave and JRPG influences!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn pixel art</strong> with expressive animation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/cb3bdac8e99aa29b639501b9f99d5697.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/cb3bdac8e99aa29b639501b9f99d5697.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/cb3bdac8e99aa29b639501b9f99d5697.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/af3db471df81c3fb2135f6998fec6789.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/af3db471df81c3fb2135f6998fec6789.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/af3db471df81c3fb2135f6998fec6789.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic approach to video game storytelling and gameplay, and an honest attempt at trying to answer the question of &quot;what if roguelites existed in 1991 for the Sega Dreamcast?&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense, precise, and rewarding platforming. Combine a variety of dashes, jumps, and sprints to reach your goal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Channel the power of the Mezameta Blade to seize corrupted souls from Tengu in the heat of combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash Tengu with a devastating hammer, unleash massive damage with a brutal greatsword.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strike from a distance with a 'Vania-inspired whip, or hurl a deadly sickle for devastating ranged attacks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/481f8ecd59e6f814b117a045100e6c53.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/481f8ecd59e6f814b117a045100e6c53.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/481f8ecd59e6f814b117a045100e6c53.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a streamlined, yet minimal loop and persistent progression, every death brings you closer to victory. Fall in battle, and the phoenix at the Twilight Perch will revive you as a stronger Bladewing,  and more prepared for what’s next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/46ad0dad5674df00c8451480864e276b.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/46ad0dad5674df00c8451480864e276b.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/46ad0dad5674df00c8451480864e276b.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > One level might have you scouring ruins for keys, another navigating vast buildings while dodging patrolling enemies, and others will launch you into the open skies of Judanest for zen-like traversal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every zone brings something new, and every challenge pulls you deeper into the heart of Judanest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/4ab6aed1fc64f522a54545283b9cb5d9.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/4ab6aed1fc64f522a54545283b9cb5d9.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/4ab6aed1fc64f522a54545283b9cb5d9.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/263c93490f48c718d9430db2aa444a0f.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/263c93490f48c718d9430db2aa444a0f.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/263c93490f48c718d9430db2aa444a0f.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/2b4a134c59ca4c2ba87fbf592f645fb3.poster.avif?t=1762482262\" width=632 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/2b4a134c59ca4c2ba87fbf592f645fb3.webm?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228490/extras/2b4a134c59ca4c2ba87fbf592f645fb3.mp4?t=1762482262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Take up arms against the evil Crow sorcerer who brainwashed your troupe.  </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You must save them all.</i></p>",
